

HAMPAS

   palo, hambalos, haplit, bugbog, halubid

   hampas
   to hit, to strike

   Hinampas niya ako sa pader.
   He threw me against the wall.

   Mukhang hinampas ang ulo.
   Looks like head was smacked.

   Humahampas sa pasigan ang mga alon.
   The waves are hitting the banks.
