MGA TAMBALANG SALITA

   hampas-lupa
   vagabond, tramp, beggar, very poor person

   hampas-bato / hampas-palo
   jobless

   hampasang-alon
   seashore, breakwater

   hampas-tikin
   afternoon sun inclined towards the west
